title: Hour 2 - NFL Updates, David Cone
itunes:title: Hour 2 - NFL Updates, David Cone
description:
Dan scrubs through updates from coaches and, of course, "Dr." Jerry Jones on the status of rosters throughout the NFL. And he talks to 5x World Series Champion and Cy young Award Winning pitcher, David Cone about Aaron Judge's Triple Crown run and exactly which homerun record he's actually chasing.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
